----- Original Message ----- 



Please take a moment to relax your mind and humble your heart to focus on 
Christ. Allow God, to be the only person on your mind while you read this 
prayer. If we can take the time to read long jokes and stories, we 
should give the same respect to this prayer. Friends that pray together, 
